episodes.title: Young, Dumb, and in a Cult! - EP 25
episodes.description: In this week’s episode, I’m talking about one of the most unhinged chapters of my life: the time I joined a cult. I was young, dumb, and fully obsessed with Freelee the Banana Girl.This is the story of how I lost the plot, drank the Kool-Aid, joined the chaos, and basically ruined my brain cells… all in the quest to be “skinny.”
